## **Typical Component Behavior**

| Component | Behavior |
| ----- | ----- |
| **Pills** | Use for status (e.g., “Sold Out”, “Required”) with consistent pill size and border |
| **Product Cards** | Size: 270x270, include image, title, price, optional icons |
| **PDP (Product Detail Page)** | Must include image gallery, SKU, pricing, availability, and CTA buttons |
| **Pagination** | Use 8px gap; include “1 of 12 results” label; center on mobile |
| **Tooltips** | Use info bubbles or hover definitions for all unfamiliar terms |

## **Responsive Design**

| Breakpoint | Min Width |
| ----- | ----- |
| XS | 390px |
| SM | 768px |
| MD | 1024px → header/nav collapses here |
| LG | 1440px |
| XL | 1728px |

* Product cards and tables must stack at XS  
* All layouts and modals must be fully responsive using Tailwind flex/grid

## **Forbidden Practices**

* No raw px or bracket syntax (w-\[250px\], mt-\[10px\])  
* No unapproved icon libraries (FontAwesome, Lucide, etc.)  
* No arbitrary Tailwind overrides or custom themes  
* No using text- to style icons—use fill- instead  
* No unscoped, in-component styles or inline style={{}} blocks  
* No custom hex or rgb color values  
* No arbitrary Tailwind syntax (e.g., w-\[150px\])  
* No inline styling or hardcoded dimensions  
* No non-system fonts or icons  
* No logic inside UI components  
* No recreating already shared components